        </item>
        <item>
            <title>开篷电动跑车 MG Cyberster 右軚版到港，两个版本一换一 52.9 万起</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/25/mg-cyberster-2/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mg-cyberster-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/25/mg-cyberster-2/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 09:00:39 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽车科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[MG Cyberster]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1258506</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>MG Cyberster 电动开篷跑车右軚版本正式在香港亮相，这款新车早前已以左軚版本在香港展出过，昨日终于迎来右軚版抵港。香港代理商亦公布了这款新车的「一换一」售价，77kWh 单马达 2WD 后驱版「一换一」车价为 HK$529,000 起，而顶级 77kWh 双马达 4WD 版「一换一」售价则为 HK$589,000 起。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258516" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1513-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1513-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1513.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258517" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1512-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1512-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1512.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>MG Cyberster 这款电动跑车以新颖设计和高效能为卖点，配备了可收放软篷设计，满足驾驶爱好者对跑车的追求，并带来电动车独特驾驶体验。Cyberster 拥有优雅而前衞的外观设计，加上高科技内装配置，成为市场上竞争力十足的选择。这款车的底盘由 Marco Fainello 设计，他曾参与 Ferrari F1 一级方程式赛车及 488 GTB 等车型的研发。该车型采用前双摇臂及后五连杆悬挂设定，让车辆在高速行驶时依然保持稳定操控。</p><p>香港版 Cyberster 有两选选择，其中 MG Cyberster 四驱 77kWh 双马达 4WD 版本，搭载前后马达，能提供 503 ps 马力及 725 Nm 扭力，0-100 km/h 加速仅需 3.2 秒。该车款配备由宁德时代提供的 77 kWh 电池，电池厚度仅 110 mm，根据 WLTP 标准测试，续航距离达 443 公里。</p><p>Cyberster 配备了标志性剪刀式车门，这款车门提供极具辨识度的外观，还内置雷达探测功能，能够检测车门顶部及车侧是否存在障碍物。车内设计同样注重细节，包括符合人体工学设计的跑车桶椅、中控台上的 7 吋屏幕。一体化数码仪表由左右两组 7 吋屏幕及中央 10.25 吋屏幕组成。中控台搭载自家 OS 系统，应用了速度高的 Snapdragon 8155 晶片及 Unreal Engine，确保操作流畅。车内还配置了 BOSE 音响系统，软篷顶可透过一键式按钮操作，能在 10 秒内完成开合，即使在车速达 50 km/h 时亦能顺利操作。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258512" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1509-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1509-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1509.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258507" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1516-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1516-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1516.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258508" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1511-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1511-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1511.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258509" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1515-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1515-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1515.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258510" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1505-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1505-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1505.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258511" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1502-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1502-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/img_1502.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>MG Cyberster 4WD 双马达版</p><p>传动：77kWh 锂电+前后马达，四驱</p><p>马力/扭力：544ps/725Nm</p><p>0 至 100km/h：3.2 秒</p><p>续航力：444km(WLTP)</p><p>尺码：4,533 x 1,912 x 1,328mm</p><p>售价：HK$589,000 起（一换一）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258513" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot_20240825_-694x324.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="324" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot_20240825_-694x324.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot_20240825_.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1258514" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot_20240825_-1-694x324.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="324" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot_20240825_-1-694x324.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/screenshot_20240825_-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/25/mg-cyberster-2/life-tech/auto/">开篷电动跑车 MG Cyberster 右軚版到港，两个版本一换一 52.9 万起</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
